title: Step it up: Does running cadence matter? Not as much as previously thought

title_detail.value: Step it up: Does running cadence matter? Not as much as previously thought

summary: Contrary to long-standing popular belief, running at a prescribed, one-size-fits-all ''optimal'' cadence doesn't play as big a role in speed and efficiency as once thought.
